---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Inicio">
  <Header />
  <main class="relative bg-background-dark overflow-hidden">
    <section class="relative min-h-[95vh] flex items-center px-6 pt-20">
      <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full max-w-4xl h-full red-glow opacity-60 pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center w-full relative z-10">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <span class="inline-block py-1.5 px-4 rounded-full bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 text-primary text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-8">Agencia Digital Boutique</span>
          <h2 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white leading-[0.95] tracking-tighter mb-8">
            Impulsamos la presencia <span class="text-primary">digital</span> de tu marca
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-xl">
            Estrategia, diseño y marketing digital integral diseñado para escalar tu negocio en un entorno competitivo.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 items-center">
            <a href="/servicios" class="px-8 h-14 bg-primary text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-primary/90 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/20 transition-all flex items-center gap-2 group">
              Ver servicios
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">arrow_forward</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/contacto" class="px-8 h-14 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-all">
              Contactar
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative order-1 lg:order-2 flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
          <div class="relative w-full max-w-lg aspect-square">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/20 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
            <img alt="Abstract digital art" class="relative z-10 w-full h-full object-cover rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border border-white/10 rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-700" src="/media/jauken.agency-04.webp" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-32 relative">
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full red-glow-strong opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-center">
          <div class="lg:col-span-5 relative z-20">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
              <div class="h-px w-8 bg-primary"></div>
              <span class="text-primary font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">Growth Engines</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-8 tracking-tighter leading-tight">
              Gestión profesional de <br/>
              <span class="relative inline-block mt-2">
                <span class="relative z-10 italic">redes sociales</span>
                <span class="absolute bottom-2 left-0 w-full h-4 bg-primary/30 -rotate-1 -z-0"></span>
                <span class="absolute -bottom-1 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-primary"></span>
              </span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg mb-12 max-w-md leading-relaxed">
              Creamos narrativas visuales que no solo atraen, sino que convierten. Transformamos tu perfil en una herramienta de ventas de alto rendimiento.
            </p>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-1 gap-6 mb-12">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 group">
                <div class="size-10 shrink-0 rounded-lg check-icon-bg border border-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-primary/30 transition-colors">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-xl font-bold">done_all</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-1">Estrategia Basada en Datos</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Planificación mensual ajustada a métricas reales de conversión.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 group">
                <div class="size-10 shrink-0 rounded-lg check-icon-bg border border-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-primary/30 transition-colors">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-xl font-bold">auto_awesome</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-1">Contenido de Vanguardia</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Diseño gráfico y edición de Reels que marcan tendencia.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 group">
                <div class="size-10 shrink-0 rounded-lg check-icon-bg border border-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-primary/30 transition-colors">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-xl font-bold">forum</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-1">Storytelling &amp; Copywriting</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Textos que conectan emocionalmente con tu audiencia ideal.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <button class="px-10 h-14 bg-primary text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/30 transition-all">
                Me interesa
              </button>
              <button class="px-6 h-14 border border-white/10 text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-white/5 transition-all">
                Casos de éxito
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-7 relative h-[600px] mt-12 lg:mt-0">
            <div class="absolute top-10 left-0 w-full lg:w-[110%] bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-3xl rounded-3xl dashboard-border p-8 shadow-2xl z-10 overflow-hidden">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-10">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                  <div class="size-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-tr from-primary to-rose-400 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-lg">analytics</span>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h5 class="text-white font-bold text-sm">Dashboard de Rendimiento</h5>
                    <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-tighter">Monitoreo en Tiempo Real</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-2">
                  <div class="size-2 rounded-full bg-white/10"></div>
                  <div class="size-2 rounded-full bg-white/10"></div>
                  <div class="size-2 rounded-full bg-white/10"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-10">
                <div class="p-5 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/5">
                  <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-bold uppercase mb-2">Alcance</p>
                  <div class="text-2xl font-black text-white">842K</div>
                  <div class="text-[10px] text-emerald-400 font-bold mt-1">↑ 14.2%</div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-5 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/5">
                  <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-bold uppercase mb-2">Clicks</p>
                  <div class="text-2xl font-black text-white">12.5K</div>
                  <div class="text-[10px] text-emerald-400 font-bold mt-1">↑ 8.4%</div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-5 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/5">
                  <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-bold uppercase mb-2">Crecimiento</p>
                  <div class="text-2xl font-black text-white">+2.4K</div>
                  <div class="text-[10px] text-emerald-400 font-bold mt-1">↑ 22%</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="h-40 w-full relative mb-6">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-end gap-2 px-2">
                  <div class="flex-1 bg-white/5 rounded-t-lg h-[40%] transition-all hover:bg-primary/40"></div>
                  <div class="flex-1 bg-white/5 rounded-t-lg h-[65%] transition-all hover:bg-primary/40"></div>
                  <div class="flex-1 bg-primary/60 rounded-t-lg h-[45%] transition-all hover:bg-primary/40"></div>
                  <div class="flex-1 bg-white/5 rounded-t-lg h-[80%] transition-all hover:bg-primary/40"></div>
                  <div class="flex-1 bg-white/5 rounded-t-lg h-[55%] transition-all hover:bg-primary/40"></div>
                  <div class="flex-1 bg-primary rounded-t-lg h-[95%] transition-all hover:bg-primary/40"></div>
                  <div class="flex-1 bg-white/5 rounded-t-lg h-[70%] transition-all hover:bg-primary/40"></div>
                  <div class="flex-1 bg-white/5 rounded-t-lg h-[60%] transition-all hover:bg-primary/40"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 w-full h-px bg-white/10"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center pt-6 border-t border-white/5">
                <div class="flex -space-x-3">
                  <div class="size-8 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-slate-800"></div>
                  <div class="size-8 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-slate-700"></div>
                  <div class="size-8 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-primary"></div>
                  <div class="size-8 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-slate-600 flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold">+12</div>
                </div>
                <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Active Campaigns</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute -bottom-6 right-0 lg:-right-12 w-72 bg-white rounded-3xl p-5 shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)] z-20 scale-90 lg:scale-100 border border-slate-100">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <div class="size-10 rounded-full bg-slate-900 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xs italic">J</div>
                <div>
                  <h6 class="text-slate-900 font-bold text-xs">jauken_agency</h6>
                  <p class="text-[9px] text-slate-400 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider">Publicidad</p>
                </div>
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined ml-auto text-slate-400 text-lg">more_horiz</span>
              </div>
              <div class="aspect-square rounded-2xl bg-slate-100 mb-4 overflow-hidden relative group">
                <img alt="Post preview" class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://placehold.co/400x400/e5e7eb/1a1a1a?text=Post+Preview" />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity flex items-center justify-center">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-3xl">play_circle</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3 px-1">
                <div class="flex gap-3">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-900 text-xl font-light">favorite</span>
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-900 text-xl font-light">chat_bubble</span>
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-900 text-xl font-light">send</span>
                </div>
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-900 text-xl font-light">bookmark</span>
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-1">
                <div class="h-1.5 w-3/4 bg-slate-100 rounded-full"></div>
                <div class="h-1.5 w-1/2 bg-slate-100 rounded-full"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute -top-10 -left-10 size-40 bg-primary/20 rounded-full blur-[80px] -z-10"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-32 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
          <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-4 text-white tracking-tighter">Nuestros Servicios</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400">Soluciones integrales para la era digital</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <div class="group p-10 rounded-[2rem] bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 hover:border-primary/40 hover:bg-white/[0.04] transition-all duration-500">
            <div class="size-14 rounded-2xl bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl">strategy</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">Estrategia</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Planes a medida analizados por expertos para maximizar el ROI de tu marca.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="group p-10 rounded-[2rem] bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 hover:border-primary/40 hover:bg-white/[0.04] transition-all duration-500">
            <div class="size-14 rounded-2xl bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl">brush</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">Diseño UI/UX</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Interfaces modernas e intuitivas que convierten visitantes en clientes fieles.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="group p-10 rounded-[2rem] bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 hover:border-primary/40 hover:bg-white/[0.04] transition-all duration-500">
            <div class="size-14 rounded-2xl bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl">campaign</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">Marketing</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Crecimiento real a través de canales digitales estratégicamente seleccionados.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="group p-10 rounded-[2rem] bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 hover:border-primary/40 hover:bg-white/[0.04] transition-all duration-500">
            <div class="size-14 rounded-2xl bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl">share</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">Social Media</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Gestión de comunidad y contenido que genera engagement y posicionamiento.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-32 px-6 relative">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 red-glow opacity-40 pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-20 gap-8">
          <div class="max-w-2xl">
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white mb-6 tracking-tighter leading-tight">Nuestros Proyectos <br/><span class="text-primary">Destacados</span></h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-400">Creatividad y tecnología para generar resultados medibles.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/portafolio" class="px-8 h-14 border border-primary/40 text-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-white font-bold rounded-xl transition-all whitespace-nowrap group flex items-center gap-2">
            Ver todo el portafolio
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">arrow_forward</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
          <div class="lg:col-span-7 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2.5rem] bg-white/5 border border-white/10 aspect-video lg:aspect-auto">
            <img alt="Project Branding" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-1000 group-hover:scale-105 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-30" src="https://placehold.co/1200x800/1a1a1a/e31e24?text=TechVision" />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/90 via-transparent to-transparent p-12 flex flex-col justify-end">
              <span class="text-primary font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">Branding &amp; Identity</span>
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-4">TechVision Rebranding</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-sm opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transform translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-all duration-500">Identidad visual disruptiva para el sector tecnológico global.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col gap-10">
            <div class="flex-1 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2.5rem] bg-white/5 border border-white/10 min-h-[300px]">
              <img alt="E-commerce Platform" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-1000 group-hover:scale-110 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-30" src="https://placehold.co/800x600/1a1a1a/e31e24?text=Urban+Style" />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 p-10 flex flex-col justify-end bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-transparent to-transparent">
                <span class="text-primary font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-2">E-commerce</span>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white">Urban Style Store</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2.5rem] bg-white/5 border border-white/10 min-h-[300px]">
              <img alt="Mobile App Design" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-1000 group-hover:scale-110 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-30" src="https://placehold.co/800x600/1a1a1a/e31e24?text=Financial+Dashboard" />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 p-10 flex flex-col justify-end bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-transparent to-transparent">
                <span class="text-primary font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-2">UI/UX App</span>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white">Financial Dashboard</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-40 px-6 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full h-full max-w-5xl red-glow-strong opacity-30 pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto relative z-10">
        <h2 class="text-6xl md:text-9xl font-black mb-10 text-white tracking-tighter leading-[0.85]">¿Listo para <br/>empezar?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-400 mb-14">Transformamos tu visión en una experiencia digital impactante.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-5">
          <button class="px-12 h-16 bg-primary text-white text-lg font-bold rounded-2xl hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/40 transition-all duration-300">
            Solicitar asesoría gratuita
          </button>
          <a href="/portafolio" class="px-12 h-16 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white text-lg font-bold rounded-2xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-all flex items-center justify-center">
            Ver proyectos
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>